extends java.lang.Object

    Version:
    1.0 Revision Notes: Full Release ISTE 121.01 CPS:ID2 Final Project Class description: The CoronosClient is the Client interface of the Coronos Timeclock Solution. The CoronosClient Class allows a user to log punches and view data pertinent to their earned wages The duplication of this code without written consent of the authors is strictly prohibited.
